{"tid":1550894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第一身訪問\"POPO揚言要姦女市民\"(有片)","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T20:13:54.000Z","uid":292893,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b08cb5d9b00900e32690d9b03891d81ccead2afe","tid":1550894,"uid":292893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:27:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/coa1l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fcoa1l&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=7828383f\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/coa1l</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58dc473d1d9dc8451b15bed93209b0ff351c975c","tid":1550894,"uid":160247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:28:16.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"0e95703665994e94b77ef5f6313d55a1c9abf8b2","tid":1550894,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:28:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e05527aad50337a8211f4c9c434875fc434a683","tid":1550894,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b316971c85e056488f9a2379e9611dbb1c57b4b","tid":1550894,"uid":278377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:30:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef3f2f1b94751872eaaf74daafcf862e7b1e5bff","tid":1550894,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414c2a7c359eb4260c74bac6f1ee8956cfa8ae21","tid":1550894,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:38:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span> <a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=0f09ef19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n今日見！</span>"},{"pid":"6cbb623f51fa4f1d7b068fcf33788f3adb460d42","tid":1550894,"uid":134206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:38:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b303bc7a68549ffb13be76b7526889a62babe5fa","tid":1550894,"uid